41
00:04:20,740 --> 00:04:21,419
I'll go back.

42
00:04:21,740 --> 00:04:22,339
Ms. Fang.

43
00:04:22,539 --> 00:04:23,659
Mr. Lu can handle things

44
00:04:23,659 --> 00:04:24,659
