45
00:04:24,659 --> 00:04:26,180
He is your husband.

46
00:04:26,180 --> 00:04:27,339
No need for you both to go.

47
00:04:27,339 --> 00:04:28,339
My husband?

48
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:29,620
Since when did I...

49
