Right.

50
00:04:35,859 --> 00:04:37,979
Mr. Lu is my husband.

51
00:04:38,539 --> 00:04:39,500
But...

52
00:04:39,500 --> 00:04:40,299
Well...

53
00:04:40,419 --> 00:04:41,140
We need to handle

54
00:04:41,140 --> 00:04:42,260
