84
00:06:16,740 --> 00:06:17,419
Gao Haiming.

85
00:06:20,140 --> 00:06:20,820
Gao Haiming.

86
00:07:37,779 --> 00:07:38,459
Miss Lin.

87
00:07:39,700 --> 00:07:41,140
