89
00:07:43,459 --> 00:07:44,008
Okay.

90
00:07:44,859 --> 00:07:45,419
Thank you.

91
00:08:29,260 --> 00:08:30,500
System has detected the Player

92
00:08:30,500 --> 00:08:31,859
