133
00:10:48,220 --> 00:10:48,740
No need.

134
00:10:48,740 --> 00:10:49,860
- It's fine. I should help.
- Wait.

135
00:10:49,860 --> 00:10:50,659
No need.

136
00:10:52,819 --> 00:10:53,419
Lin Huan'er.

137
00:10:54,460 --> 00:10:55,100
Lin Huan'er.

138
00:11:02,299 --> 00:11:02,899
I...

139
