246
00:18:18,059 --> 00:18:19,619
Last night, did you...

247
00:18:19,619 --> 00:18:21,660
Stop! Don't imagine things.

248
00:18:21,660 --> 00:18:22,819
I'm going to work now. Bye.

249
00:18:23,299 --> 00:18:23,819
Hello.

250
00:18:27,020 --> 00:18:28,220
